    "question_id" : 61483057,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This failes likely due to an artifact downloaded earlier (in my case .m2/repository/org/geotools/geotools/19.1/geotools-19.1.pom) containing this as a specific repo, maybe even retrieved from a thirdparty repo.</p>\n\n<p>Check your local artifacts for references to the repository, e.g. by this brute force approach:</p>\n\n<pre><code>grep -nr \"central.maven.org\" ~/.m2/repository/\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Replacing/removing the dependency solved the issue.</p>\n"
  } ],
